{"tid":916798,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"佩雷斯玻璃入眼 泰維斯中胡椒噴霧 雙雙送院治療","createTime":"2018-11-26T02:56:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-26T03:25:25.000Z","uid":54373,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"cdef03d628b9d128c7899e3c8412e9324fc4e8ef","tid":916798,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T02:56:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/WginHvqMFZw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FWginHvqMFZw&d=azl4pq8h0FMwvaZgJeX2tkjIoeaDRyeQRMy%2FzT52C%2Fo%3D&h=fe4a868f\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/WginHvqMFZw</a><br />\n小保加隊巴被襲擊片段<br />\n<br />\n南美自由盃決賽次回合未開賽已成鬧劇，作客的小保加乘坐隊巴，仍未抵達到河床主場就被河床球迷以石頭、胡椒彈攻擊，兩個球員需送院及多人嘔吐。南美足協兩次延遲開賽時間後，兩間球會會長達成共識，賽會同意延期至周一凌晨4︰00再戰。<br />\n<br />\n南美自由盃決賽首回合河床作客以2︰2逼和小保加，次回合原訂於周日凌晨4︰00開賽。不過小保加的隊巴仍未抵達河床主場紀念碑球場時，已被河床球迷以石頭、木棍、胡椒彈擲向隊巴，最少三隻車窗被打爛，小保加球員都掩住口鼻下車。<br />\n<br />\n小保加隊巴往球場時，被河床球迷襲擊。（路透社）<br />\n<br />\n小保加隊長柏保路佩雷斯（Pablo PEREZ）因玻璃碎入眼受傷，與干沙路拿馬度送院。前鋒泰維斯因胡椒彈引致不適，需要職員扶住步入更衣室，阿根廷傳媒指包括泰維斯在內的小保加球員在更衣室嘔吐。泰維斯接受訪問時認為球賽應改期︰「我們不能作賽，卻一度被迫上陣。柏保路在醫院治療後回來，眼部被紗布包住，另一隊友被割傷，被氣體影響後我們才剛剛可以如常呼吸，球隊不能在這個狀態下比賽。」即使河床主帥加拿度不同意開賽，南美足協仍多番只延遲開賽時間，希望繼續比賽。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2133314/org/edadeb97cfbba4e855133a9d877f195c.jpg/IBD4QDPgGT4DK8jiJLyWf6kb9aXhqM0EuqWd87qlnfM?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2133314%2Forg%2Fedadeb97cfbba4e855133a9d877f195c.jpg%2FIBD4QDPgGT4DK8jiJLyWf6kb9aXhqM0EuqWd87qlnfM%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=5a2b230e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n自由盃賽事組織主席杜明基斯（Alejandro Dominguez）最終稱在兩間球會的會長一致同意下，決定將賽事延期︰「他們都作出君子協定，由於一隊不能作賽，另一隊不希望與不在正常狀態的宿敵較技，賽事只好延期。」次回合賽事已延至周一凌晨4︰00舉行。前阿根廷戰神巴迪斯圖達形容事件可恥，「再一次在全世界面前令人失望，很可悲。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2133313/org/16338cb799ce4ac5ff32d54e316cb372.jpg/oFLFHX2ZH4KRj0MV86yilOyoZRpalNtHnFULdJxVC3Q?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2133313%2Forg%2F16338cb799ce4ac5ff32d54e316cb372.jpg%2FoFLFHX2ZH4KRj0MV86yilOyoZRpalNtHnFULdJxVC3Q%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=015746cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n泰維斯疑受胡椒噴霧攻擊，需要職員扶住入更衣室。（路透社）"},{"pid":"52c8992e0865f66a2bcd050458ac4ada96687bfc","tid":916798,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T02:58:56.000Z","msg":"南美狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bb73d4d7c364764c8fd4357e7668e92e81410d9","tid":916798,"uid":5649,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T02:59:38.000Z","msg":"點解唔係佩雷斯主席"},{"pid":"f39454d2c8a9d101b585f5ba8d181ae0356218e4","tid":916798,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"52c8992e0865f66a2bcd050458ac4ada96687bfc","tid":916798,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T02:58:56.000Z","msg":"南美狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T02:59:46.000Z","msg":"G持!<br />\n熱血球迷應該係咁"},{"pid":"ea13a0d26b248894d0b42621018a94cd6e4f72b8","tid":916798,"uid":52571,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"5bb73d4d7c364764c8fd4357e7668e92e81410d9","tid":916798,"uid":5649,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T02:59:38.000Z","msg":"點解唔係佩雷斯主席"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T03:03:42.000Z","msg":"收皮啦"},{"pid":"0c8401ac3a0d88a44185705fe60776754f62f7b1","tid":916798,"uid":158145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5bb73d4d7c364764c8fd4357e7668e92e81410d9","tid":916798,"uid":5649,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T02:59:38.000Z","msg":"點解唔係佩雷斯主席"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T03:09:43.000Z","msg":"笑左笑埋右"},{"pid":"9eed96724f56b651a3469f9f9d17a85249b4860d","tid":916798,"uid":54373,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0c8401ac3a0d88a44185705fe60776754f62f7b1","tid":916798,"uid":158145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5bb73d4d7c364764c8fd4357e